ies because of the full service it offers its clients. There is rarely a task too large or too small for this cleaning company to handle. It will tackle all basic cleaning tasks such as dusting, vacuuming and trash removal. It will also clean all restrooms and restock supplies. Additionally, the company completes many major cleaning projects such as stripping and waxing floors, cleaning carpets, and cleaning blinds and upholstery.","Another advantage of this cleaning company is that its staff is trained to follow all cleaning and safety guidelines to clean medical facilities. The company complies with all medical cleaning standards to ensure that you will pass your inspections. The company offers all its employees Hepatitis B vaccinations before they enter your medical facility. All employees must wear gloves, and trash bags are not allowed to come into contact with their bodies.","<em>Recommendation Commercial Cleaning Service for Large Businesses – </em><a href=\"https://www.business.com/reviews/office-pride/\"><em>OfficePride</em></a>","<strong>Best Commercial Cleaning Service for Small Businesses</strong>","Vanguard Cleaning Systems will perform basic cleaning tasks around your facility, which is perfect for small businesses. The crew will sanitize all restrooms, vacuum floors, remove trash and more. However, if you want a more in-depth cleaning job, they will clean carpets, buff and wax floors, and even wash windows.","One of the advantages of Vanguard Cleaning Systems is it will create a customized cleaning plan for your office. Each office is unique and has different cleaning needs. Vanguard Cleaning Systems recognizes this and will work with you to meet your needs.","<em>Recommendation Commercial Cleaning Service for Small Businesses – </em><a href=\"https://www.business.com/reviews/vanguard-cleaning-systems/\"><em>Vanguard Cleaning Systems</em></a>","<strong>Best Commercial Cleaning Service for Floors</strong>","Along with providing services for small and large businesses, OfficePride specializes in floor cleaning. OfficePride can handle a variety of floor-care needs, including stripping, sealing and waxing floors, vacuuming, and mopping. It has trained employees who can buff, deep scrub, refinish and deodorize floors. They can also remove spots on carpets and perform color repairs. Their floor care is much more advanced and thorough than many similar cleaning companies, which is a large benefit to using this service.","<em>Recommendation Commercial Cleaning Service for Floors – OfficePride</em>","<strong>Best Commercial Cleaning Service for Outdoor Maintenance</strong>","Not many commercial cleaning services will offer both indoor and outdoor cleaning, but Stratus Building Solutions does. This cleaning company will perform lawn care and outdoor maintenance around your facility in addition to providing janitorial services inside your building. The outdoor maintenance services include mowing, edging, trimming, mulching and taking care of flower beds. This is one of the best advantages to this service and is a feature that sets it apart from most commercial cleaning services.","<em>Recommendation Commercial Cleaning Service for Outdoor Maintenance – </em><a href=\"https://www.business.com/reviews/stratus-building-solutions/\"><em>Stratus Building Solutions</em></a>","<strong>To Consider When Selecting a Commercial Cleaning Service</strong>","The best office cleaning companies will take care of all of your building&#39;s cleaning needs. They will perform basic cleaning tasks such as sanitizing the restroom and vacuuming the floors, and you can add additional services such as carpet cleaning, window washing, buffing the floor and more. The best services are flexible and willing to perform the job you need done.","Be sure to look for a janitorial service that has experience cleaning your type of building. Some services will clean offices, churches, schools, banks, hospitals and even stadiums and event centers, while others will clean only offices or schools. You need to carefully look into the industries the company will service before you invest too much time looking into the company.","Janitorial services must be flexible and cater to the needs of your business. If you have long or unusual business hours, you need a service that is willing to work around your schedule. Additionally, many services provide green cleaning options such as recycling programs, so you can enjoy not just a clean office, but an environmentally safe office as well.","The best commercial cleaning companies require all of their workers to dress in a uniform so you know who they are and why they are walking around your office. This also allows you to easily see if they are in restricted areas or going through items without permission."]},"id":"9a7557c4-5b20-4db4-9ec3-26db3370ecdc","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Related Product Reviews"},"id":"56f81b57-b406-4bb3-af1d-58b04fac505e","type":"heading"},{"data":{"items":["<a href=\"http://www.buyerzone.com/facilities/commercial-cleaning-services/rfq-commercial-cleaning-services/?publisherId=21232&amp;publisherTypeId=1788\">Office Pride</a>","<a href=\"http://www.buyerzone.com/facilities/commercial-cleaning-services/rfq-commercial-cleaning-services/?publisherId=21232&publisherTypeId=1788\">Vanguard</a>","<a href=\"http://www.buyerzone.com/facilities/commercial-cleaning-services/rfq-commercial-cleaning-services/?publisherId=21232&amp;publisherTypeId=1788\">Jani-King</a>","<a href=\"http://www.buyerzone.com/facilities/commercial-cleaning-services/rfq-commercial-cleaning-services/?publisherId=21232&amp;publisherTypeId=1788\">Anago Cleaning Systems</a>","<a href=\"http://www.buyerzone.com/facilities/commercial-cleaning-services/rfq-commercial-cleaning-services/?publisherId=21232&amp;publisherTypeId=1788\">ABM</a>","<a href=\"http://www.buyerzone.com/facilities/commercial-cleaning-services/rfq-commercial-cleaning-services/?publisherId=21232&amp;publisherTypeId=1788\">Clea